summary: This is a calendar entry from the Ghislaine Maxwell case scheduling the administration of juror questionnaires at the Foley Square Courthouse in November 2021. It indicates the court's preparation for jury selection in Maxwell's trial.

events.title: Maxwell Juror Questionnaire Administration Start
events.description: Scheduled start date for administering juror questionnaires in the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.

events.title: Maxwell Juror Questionnaire Administration End
events.description: Scheduled end date for administering juror questionnaires in the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.

keyFacts: The document is a calendar entry related to the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.
It schedules the administration of juror questionnaires from November 4 to November 6, 2021.
The event was to take place at the 40 Foley Square Courthouse.
The calendar entry was created on August 27, 2021, and modified on November 10, 2021.
This indicates active pre-trial preparation for jury selection in Maxwell's case.
